::Prowl/Killer/Striker/Ramulus/Ramhorn/Smokescreen::

Prowl's eyes widen as he recieves Dinobot's transmission. His wings twitch, 
causing his to miss his dive at Sixshot.

"The Alliance captured them?! We-AAAAH!!!"

Jetpack on full power, Killer smashes into Prowl, the predacon's sword going 
into Prowl's side. Prowl kicks Killer slightly away, then fires a few acid 
pellets at him.

"We have a battle here at the Ark, Dinobot," he yells quickly into his 
comm-link, "Get back here. We'll need to get equipment to get Iron Raptor and 
Tav back."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker slashes again at Hades. He growls. The newcomers were ignoring quite 
alot of damage (Hint, hint, Inferno).
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus continues to fire at Sixshot.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Seeing Shadow Wing fall, Smokescreen runs over to her, grabbing her by the 
leg and begining to drag her toward the Ark.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramhorn takes out another charge, throwing it at Shuko.
